    "body": "## Problem\n\nwindows \"oldtest\" ci fails with:\n\n    Assertion failed: process_title, file src\\win\\util.c, line 412\n\nThis happens in the \"Post job cleanup\" phase, after our runner already exited.\n\nSymptom was fixed by libuv 1.52.1 https://github.com/nodejs/node/issues/58695 , but we have already updated to that.\n\nIt's probably not related to a `msys2/setup-msys2` change because we have it pinned for several weeks: https://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/df8d98173cbc03d78da18fee7f31f130db2c9e44/.github/workflows/test_windows.yml#L77\n\nbut it might be a change in `pacman` packages?\n\n## Next steps\n\n1. check if the MSYS2 runtime packages updated recently (`pacman -Q` in the CI)                                                                                                                                                                \n2. check https://github.com/msys2/setup-msys2\n3. check the GHA Windows runner image changelog                                                                                                                                                                                              \n4. check https://github.com/actions/setup-node\n",
